    problem: `The existing experience lacked a unified information architecture, forcing visitors to switch between multiple apps, websites, and physical signage. Key issues included:\n\n• No single source of truth for schedules, attractions and real-time updates\n• VIP journey planning required manual intervention from staff\n• Multi-language (Arabic/English) support was inconsistent\n• Navigation was overwhelming given the scale of content`,
